description: Setsuna, who has just become Cure Passion, doesn`t have a place to go back to. While she`s walking down the street, she meets Love, who`s going to a restaurant with her parents.

titles.title: Setsuna no Kunou: Watashi wa Nakama ni Narenai!
The Passionate Pretty Cure Is Born! My Name Is Cure Passion!
せつなの苦悩 私は仲間になれない!
